                                        sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                        text="&lt;p>Koinis, Filippos; Kotsakis, Athanasios; Georgoulias, Vasileios. Transl Lung Cancer Res. 2016 Feb; 5(1): 39–50. Small Cell Lung Cancer (SCLC): No Treatment Advances in Recent Years. Accessed November 13, 2017. Available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4758968/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;Small Lung Cancer&quot;>https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4758968/&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>American Cancer Society. Key Statistics for Small Cell Lung Cancer. Accessed November 13, 2017. Available &lt;a title=&quot;American Cancer Society: Ley Statistics&quot; href=&quot;https://www.cancer.org/cancer/small-cell-lung-cancer/about/key-statistics.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>https://www.cancer.org/cancer/small-cell-lung-cancer/about/key-statistics.html&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>American Cancer Society. Small Cell Lung Cancer Survival Rates, by Stage. Accessed November 13, 2017. Available &lt;a title=&quot;American Cancer Society Small Cell Lung Cancer&quot; href=&quot;https://www.cancer.org/cancer/small-cell-lung-cancer/detection-diagnosis-staging/survival-rates.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>https://www.cancer.org/cancer/small-cell-lung-cancer/detection-diagnosis-staging/survival-rates.html&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Yu-Juan Jin, Chao Zheng, Hong-Bin Ji. Recent Advances in Cancer Research and Therapy, 2012. 20.8. Perspective. Molecular and Cellular Characteristics of Small Cell Lung Cancer: Implications for Molecular-Targeted Cancer Therapy.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                        textIsRich="true"/>
